metadata.name: #1 Netherlands Zaanse Schans
metadata.description:
Born in the 1970s in Germany, I developed a passion for photography early on. These are mainly landscapes and special things that should take the viewer on a multifaceted journey. The focus is on the beauty of the moment, which always inspires my international collectors as well as myself.

Edition: 1/1
